      "source": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Holliswood%2C_Queens"
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "text": "The neighborhood’s streets were designed by the Grenoble Realty Company in 1905, featuring winding layouts and Latin or Spanish names like Palo Alto and Como.",
      "sourceSentenceIds": [
